---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service - AI Tools HQ"
  description="Terms of service for AI Tools HQ. Read our terms and conditions for using the site."
>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p>Last updated: January 2025</p>
    </header>

    <section class="content">
      <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing and using AI Tools HQ, you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms
        of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our website.
      </p>

      <h2>Use of Content</h2>
      <p>
        All content on AI Tools HQ, including reviews, comparisons, and articles, is provided
        for informational purposes only. You may not:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Reproduce or redistribute our content without permission</li>
        <li>Use our content for commercial purposes without authorization</li>
        <li>Scrape or automatically collect data from our site</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        AI Tools HQ provides reviews and information about third-party AI tools. We are not
        affiliated with these tools unless explicitly stated. Our reviews reflect our honest
        opinions based on testing, but:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Tools and their features may change after our review</li>
        <li>Your experience may differ from ours</li>
        <li>We cannot guarantee the accuracy of all information</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Affiliate Relationships</h2>
      <p>
        AI Tools HQ participates in affiliate programs. When you click certain links and make
        purchases, we may earn commissions. This does not affect the price you pay. Our reviews
        are independent of affiliate relationships.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Websites</h2>
      <p>
        Our site contains links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content,
        privacy practices, or terms of these external sites. Visiting them is at your own risk.
      </p>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        AI Tools HQ and its owners are not liable for any damages arising from your use of
        this website or reliance on its content. This includes direct, indirect, incidental,
        or consequential damages.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this
        page. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .content h2:first-child {
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content ul {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content a {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .content a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-page {
      padding: 7rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
